## Quick Capture

### Add a Thought
Just write in [[Personal/Thoughts]] — no format required. Date it if you want.

### Queue a Prompt
Add to [[Personal/Prompts]] with this format:
```markdown
## [Short Title]
- **Priority:** P0/P1/P2/P3
- **Status:** pending

[Your prompt/instruction here]
```

### Park an Idea
Add to [[Personal/Ideas]] with minimal detail — flesh out later.

