## Dataview Queries

### Pending Prompts Count

```dataviewjs
const prompts = dv.page("Personal/Prompts");
if (prompts) {
  const content = await dv.io.load(prompts.file.path);
  const pendingCount = (content.match(/status:\s*pending/gi) || []).length;
  dv.paragraph(`**Pending Prompts:** ${pendingCount}`);
}
```

